---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { fade, slide, ViewTransitions } from "astro:transitions";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms and conditions - Dynamic Total Services"
  content="Terms and conditions of Dynamic Total Services. - We understand the dynamic nature of the mining industry. With our flexible workforce management, you can easily adjust your staffing levels based on project demands, seasonal variations, or unforeseen events. We provide you with the agility to optimise productivity while minimising overhead costs."
>
  <main
    transition:name="main"
    transition:animate={slide({ duration: "0.4s" })}
    class="min-h-[80vh] overflow-x-hidden"
  >
    <header class="m-auto py-8 bg-secondaryBg pt-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center text-white">
        Terms and Conditions
      </h1>
    </header>
    <div class="py-9 px-3 flex md:px-14 lg:px-32 flex-col justify-center">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Acceptance of Terms</h3>
      <p class="mb-2">
        By accessing our website or using our services, you acknowledge that you
        have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms and
        Conditions, as well as our Privacy Policy.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Services Description</h3>
      <p class="mb-2">
        Dynamic Total Services specializes in recruiting skilled workers and
        providing outsourcing solutions for businesses. We connect employers
        with qualified candidates and offer tailored outsourcing options to meet
        your business needs.
      </p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">User Responsibilities</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          You must provide accurate and up-to-date information when registering
          for an account or using our services.
        </li>
        <li>
          You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your
          account credentials.
        </li>
        <li>
          You agree not to use our services for any unlawful or unauthorized
          purposes.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Job Postings and Candidates</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          Employers are solely responsible for the accuracy of their job
          postings.
        </li>
        <li>
          We do not guarantee the availability or suitability of candidates for
          specific job positions.
        </li>
        <li>
          Candidates' qualifications and references should be verified by
          employers before hiring.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Payments</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          Fees for our services will be outlined in separate agreements with
          clients.
        </li>
        <li>
          All payments should be made according to the terms specified in our
          invoices.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Intellectual Property</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          The content on our website, including text, graphics, logos, and
          images, is protected by copyright and other intellectual property
          laws.
        </li>
        <li>
          You may not use, reproduce, modify, or distribute our content without
          our explicit permission.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Privacy</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          Your privacy is important to us. Please refer to our Privacy Policy to
          understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Limitation of Liability</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          We are not responsible for any damages, losses, or liabilities arising
          from the use of our website or services.
        </li>
        <li>
          We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of
          information provided by users.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Termination</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your account if you
          violate these Terms and Conditions or engage in any unauthorized or
          unlawful activities.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Modifications</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          We reserve the right to modify or update these Terms and Conditions at
          any time.
        </li>
        <li>
          Any changes will be effective upon posting on our website. It is your
          responsibility to review these terms periodically.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Limitation of Liability</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          We are not responsible for any damages, losses, or liabilities arising
          from the use of our website or services.
        </li>
        <li>
          We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of
          information provided by users.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-2">Governing Law</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-2">
        <li>
          These Terms and Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance
          with the laws of Australia.
        </li>
        <li>
          Any disputes arising from these terms will be subject to the exclusive
          jurisdiction of the courts in Australia.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-center mt-4">
        Thank you for choosing Dynamic Total Services. If you have any questions
        or concerns about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at
        <a
          class="hover:underline"
          href="mailto:info@dynamictotalservices.com.au"
        >
          info@dynamictotalservices.com.au</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
